{"type": "article", "id": 56382, "title": "这款吸湿排汗足弓加压的袜子，原是为厨师做的｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-09-13T22:34:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 23350, "name": "DesignByThem"}, {"id": 52733, "name": "Eskayel"}, {"id": 52734, "name": "Milligram Studio"}, {"id": 52735, "name": "ODO"}, {"id": 52736, "name": "Hedley＆Bennett"}, {"id": 52737, "name": "Richer Poorer"}, {"id": 52738, "name": "Joel Escalona"}, {"id": 24685, "name": "Marcel Sigel"}, {"id": 52739, "name": "Keita Suzuki"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 119, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180913213936Z4Rmx3e9ylQOTcEP.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s7 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Quartet of Colorful, Modern Socks by Hedley＆Bennett X Richer Poorer</h3><p>最近，加州厨师服及用品品牌 Hedley＆Bennett 和服装品牌 Richer Poorer 合作推出专为厨师设计的袜子。这一系列更有四种款式，由双方团队共同设计。袜子运用控温科技，结合网眼排汗孔洞和吸湿排汗材料，帮助待在高温厨房里的厨师降温。另外还在袜子底部增厚、足弓加压，让需要久站的厨师更舒适些。</p><p>Hedley＆Bennett 的创始人 Ellen Bennett 表示，这个系列的袜子，灵感源自 20 世纪中期建筑师 Luis Barragán 和艺术家 Frida Kahlo 的作品，也杂糅了两位创作者的特点，比如各类线条、形状、阴影和纹理的组合，和充满活力的色彩的混搭，明亮多彩。售价 16 美元，<a href=\"https://www.hedleyandbennett.com/collections/h-b-x-richer-poorer\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214013vZnmiJRNczIWjOpX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214013Nu8xSKIpmP1AGstZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809132140152nPZJpqBiDTGAroF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214015riBT93D08ZyISnsb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214016wpK3o12HOy97STNQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214016LKkarp6mJ2su3NyY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.350781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>FORM Geometric Lighting by Milligram Studio and ODO</h3><p>墨尔本 Milligram Studio 与 One Design Office 合作开发了一系列试图探索形状的灯光 FORM Geometric。不同形状的组合，唤起了一种游戏感。组合中较小的球体嵌在几何底座雕刻的凹口内，几何底座有圆柱形、矩形和三角形三种，提供黑、白、粉红和蓝绿四种哑光色调。</p><p>按照设计师的意图，FORM Geometric 系列既可以单独使用，也可以组合使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214043KU7P8yB9S5t1OefV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214043BR648sE2XUeG9uk0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214044JRrZq8L640pwh2lS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809132140441UJ0PYcKRkLi5uyD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.milligram.studio/lighting-collection-launches-at-life-instyle-melbourne/#more-1022\" rel=\"nofollow\">Milligram Studio</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Kaenjusai Watering Can by Keita Suzuki</h3><p>日本知名设计师 Keita Suzuki 设计出一款浇水壶，以铜和天然木材制作，铜具有杀菌的功能，能保持清水的洁净。当然，这款浇水壶的独特之处，还在于其手柄和壶嘴之间有着精密的角度，浇水时容易操作，避免倒泄，设计非常细心。</p><p>手柄处以核桃木制作，为家中提供温暖的触感，底部刻有树木图案，做工也非常精致有心思。售价 250 美元，<a href=\"https://www.odetothings.com/collections/all/products/kaenjusai-watering-can\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214138cRdeGA3ZLIfD1b7v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214138DrSk6W9HfYV4JqAl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214140ZfOCPmTVegG7Xx1R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214157LGmDNHoVKvpJfZrc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.odetothings.com/collections/all/products/kaenjusai-watering-can\" rel=\"nofollow\">ode to things</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Jamaa Series Rug Collection by Eskayel</h3><p>今年早些时候，纽约纺织品牌 Eskayel 推出了 Jamaa II 壁纸和纺织品系列，灵感来自马拉喀什和高阿特拉斯山脉附近的沙漠景观。最近，Eskayel 又推出了同系列地毯，采用改编自原创化作的抽象图案，意在诠释摩洛哥活力的一面。</p><p>色彩缤纷的地毯由手工编织的丝绸和精美的美利奴羊毛制成，配有 30 毫米细的竹丝地毯，描出纹理和深度。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214225dXq2yeNpoSgUVwCJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809132142250Or8ERWNkxizvcIn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214226EOFfWBQMcwK5RJiL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214225MDS8scXH7buoGYOK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748437\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214226Bugd2porCOcikUsI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809132142263UVDzrIAnBYEFZPh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744531\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://eskayel.com/product-category/new-arrivals/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eskayel</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Soda Chair by Marcel Sigel for DesignByThem</h3><p>澳洲独立设计品牌 DesignByThem 推出了一款可堆叠的座椅 Soda，出自工业设计师 Marcel Sigel 之手。设计师表示，这把椅子的结构灵感源自 19 世纪的经典曲木椅子，在突出醒目的结构和线条的同时，又能保持极简主义风格，既适合放在阳台、露台等户外环境使用，也可用于咖啡馆或是家中。</p><p>弯曲的粉末涂层不锈钢管勾勒出其框架，嵌于其中的金属网，构成座椅和靠背。售价 477 澳元，<a href=\"https://www.designbythem.com/products/soda-chair?variant=12496050258008\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214318S8TmVsegOJlBb2K9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214318KMqrlN9GRcwPJfjn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214321QewJK98xY4CviRps.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214321oQS4u5ce7lzZBy1E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913214321PdZl3UpEtzC0Vg7v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.032812\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：DesignByThem</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Florete by Joel Escalona</h3><p>在墨西哥流行艺术博物馆组织的 arte / sano÷artistas 5.0 双年展上，墨西哥艺术家、设计师 Joel Escalona 创造了一款名为 Florete 的花器，与其合作的是大师级工匠 Napoleón Pérez Pamat。</p><p>这个看起来结构奇妙的物体，一眼看上去可能会让人联想到 Artemide 的 Nessino 台灯的形状，但它的实际功能就是花器。该花器完全由铜制成，底座上刻有钻石图案。设计师在描述这件作品时表示，Joel Escalona 说他是在尝试挑战设计和工艺之间的界限。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913215323Tyncozr1HKFed4GN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913215326ja3tybHFZ4sGh8f1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913215331K2yfpLonuJ4RYd0O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913215333gHPiW3cDG4SKTkl8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}